caption: A single book, with a rich brown cover, begins to glide smoothly across the polished wooden surface of the table. The gentle motion creates a soft, whispering sound as the book moves steadily from one side to the other. The light reflects off the table, highlighting the book's journey, while the room remains calm and still, emphasizing the serene yet curious movement of the book.
